    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Despite achieved credibility levels falling below required levels for all assessed factors and six factors remaining not-assessed, the submission is accepted for regulatory filing with the understanding that outstanding gaps are documented as open items requiring resolution prior to device clearance. Monte Carlo UQ results demonstrate that 95th-percentile hemolysis predictions remain below the clinical threshold. The mesh independence study supports spatial discretization adequacy, though its formal evidence artifact was not linked in this package. Remaining gaps at MRL 5 are acknowledged.",
